-- Spain's Caixabank to replace CEO with CFO - source
-- By Sarah Morris
-- Mon Jun 30, 2014 12:07PM EDT
-- None



MADRID, June 30 (Reuters) - Spain's Caixabank <CABK.MC> is to replace its Chief Executive Juan Maria Nin with Chief Financial Officer Gonzalo Gortazar, a source with knowledge of the matter told Reuters on Monday.

